name: Premier Home Health Care Services, Inc.

narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Premier Home Health Care Services, Inc. is a Home Health provider based in New York, NY. From 2018-02 through 2022-09, this provider received $124K in Medicaid payments across 2K claims serving 328 beneficiaries, billing 1 distinct procedure codes.
